        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Labeling & Organization Systems</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Use permanent markers or printed labels to identify contents: "Christmas 2026," "CNY Lights," "Raya Banners." Color-coded stickers speed up finding items when the season returns. This organization system turns chaos into efficiency.</p>

        <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface mb-4">Cushioning Materials for Fragile Items</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Wrap delicate ornaments, figurines, and ceramic decorations in bubble wrap or crinkle fill before placing in used boxes. This protects against shifting and damage during the 6–12 month storage period.</p>
